My Last 2 Days

gday fans
thought id write in here again.. no real reason.. im just bored. i am absolutely wrecked at the moment, mostly coz of the things iv dun over yesterday and 2day. Yesterday, i had 2 get up rly early 2 go 2 swimmin trainin.(im sposed 2 do trainin 9 times a week coz im in the state squad). we did only 4km that morning, but when u add that to the 4km i did later that arvo, then that prty much stuffed me. today, i went down to the cricket nets with a mate and we stayed down ther in the 35 degree heat for like 3 hours, me goin prty much non stop bowling. thats all iv dun.. i know not much, but when uv dun nuthin 4 the last 2 months, small things get the better of u.
newayz, leave me comments and messages often, and hope 2 talk 2 yaz all soon

ITS TIME TO ROCK... AND RIDE!!!!

how many people out ther watched the tv show 'biker mice from mars' when they were little. i was talkin 2 ppl at work and how we were all obsessed with it when we were younger. but then, half my friends from school havnt even heard of it. iv just watched the 1st 3 eps on you tube, and it is fuckin the maddest show EVER!!! its hard to believe sumthin from back in the early 90s was so quality. i found all my old figurines 2 lol. thers also a new comeback series goin now.. supposedly on channel 10, so im gunna hav 2 check this out.

who hates early mornings?

argghhh i hate early mornings. theyr so.. early.. and no1 is ever online. over this week i wil hav been up pre-530 4 out of 7 days. 2 bcoz of swimming, and then the retards that do the roster at my work gave me 2 'open' shifts, which means i hav 2 start at 430 both 2moro and the next day. its not even in my list of available times.. it makes me angry..

DAAAAAAAAAARRRGHH!!!!!

ahmg im so angry right now.. i just got home from work.. which was a 6.5 hour shift starting at 430 in the morning. this would be enuf 2 make ne1 angry, but then i also had 2 get up early 4 swimmin yesterday and hav work 2morro at 430 agen, even when it isnt in my availabilities 2 work. but, thats not all. after enduring those tough still-dark early moning hours, towards the end of my shift the front crew were gettin rly shitty, and some of the back crew were just plain fuckin idiots, and i was caught in the middle. i was bein abused by managers coz i couldnt do the things i was sposed 2 do bcoz i was waiting on sum1 else 2 do wat they had 2 do, then the front crew were just yelling for no particular reason (this seems 2 b happening more and more often) and the back crew goin so slowly an it was so crowded.. i felt like getttin a baseball bat and relieving my anger on the closest object. if i hav 2 put up with that agen 2morro.. god help them

a surprisingly gd day

well the way the day started, i wouldve never thought it would end with me this.. uh.. with lack of a better word.. happy. had 2 get up at 430 4 work and that was lame, but i didnt get hardly ne xustomers, 6 in the first 2 and a half hours. it went fairly slowly, and changeover was mad. but then i got forced 2 stay back an hour, so i finished at 1230, and was practically dying on my feet... and very angry. eventually i got off, but then had 2 sit and listen 2 my manager rant for 10 minutes. i came home and tried 2 sleep, but failed miserably. eventually it was time 4 bball, and i havnt played in 10 weeks. this was also a team in men c div, who i hadnt played 4 before. i knew most of them tho, and it gd 2 play with a whole bunch of ppl who hav coaching certs. i moved thru a lot of positions. my shooting was rly off.. as expected, but ended up with 6 points, 2 of those coming from a mad steal. i also had the advantage that i was fit from swimming all thru the holis, so i could run 4 ages. they eventually subbed me with 6 min 2 go, but i didnt rly need it. i was just running flat out the whole game. we lost, but i hav high hopes for this team, coz its a gd bunch, we just havnt figured out the proper positions yet. its so good 2 b bak at bball

first day back at skool

elo all.
today.. the day i have been dreading for weeks, has been. and u know what? it was a fuckin MAD day. it was great. today was the day i went back to skool, and we had 2 hav a dbl period of homegroup first. but it was great. me and my mates just talked and heard alot of stories, and i laughed so much. i then had frees period 3 and 4, so me and a bunch of guys from another homegroup went and played 500 in the library. then i had pe with my mate yops, and it was mad, we just played dogeball, hockey and bashball. lots of runnin around and laughin. gd fun.even my bitch homegroup teacher was fairly decent today, so hopefully it will stay that way. then 2morro we r gettin some grid iron goin at luch time, and i hav vis comm, english language and homegroup, so should be another bludge day 4 me 2moro

BBALL WIN!!

AHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!! so happy right now. i just played bball, and ive been in a team full of fairly inexperienced ppl, and my dad put me in this team to get sum experience in2 the team. we hav bn on a bit of a drought with wins.. and finally won 2night the final score was 37 - 22, with the game high score of 17 going to yours truely evry1 pulled 2getha and we had mad passing and shooting 2day. some of my shots were soooo nice.. just over the rim with a splash of the net.. oh its bn a while since iv shot that well. i also did alot of hangtime layups, where id run up, take my steps froom the foul line then jump up, wait for them to fall below me, and roll it of the tips of my fingers. i also got a buch of rejections and steals, and also a reverse layup. good game all round
